e18a64dd-b951-4016-b3dd-c1c1da15f42d.title: Ned
e18a64dd-b951-4016-b3dd-c1c1da15f42d.text:
Why, hello there, lad. Me friends call me Ned. I was a
man of the sea, but it's past me now. Could I be
making or selling you some rope?

options.text: Ned, could you make other things from wool?
Yes, I would like some rope.
No thanks Ned, I don't need any.

81b345f8-7f91-424c-aec8-2433718353cf.title: <player>
81b345f8-7f91-424c-aec8-2433718353cf.text: No thanks Ned, I don't need any.

7c01adf9-5fb5-4064-9d8a-e84c54882bfe.title: Ned
7c01adf9-5fb5-4064-9d8a-e84c54882bfe.text:
Well, old Neddy is always here if you do. Tell your
friends. I can always be using the business.

59cf1651-a4d4-4539-b10b-a2ac6ee8520b.title: <player>
59cf1651-a4d4-4539-b10b-a2ac6ee8520b.text: Yes, I would like some rope.

62ec140c-67b1-4984-a237-fabd4faebb15.title: Ned
62ec140c-67b1-4984-a237-fabd4faebb15.text:
Well, I can sell you some rope for 15 coins. Or I can
be making you some if you gets me 4 balls of wool. I
strands them together I does, makes em strong.

93d0ac23-a63f-4d43-a493-a63a99d954d0.title: <player>
93d0ac23-a63f-4d43-a493-a63a99d954d0.text: I thought you needed hemp or jute.

67676199-e2cf-46b1-8156-018e5f65be4c.title: Ned
67676199-e2cf-46b1-8156-018e5f65be4c.text: Do you want some rope or not?

options.text: Okay, please sell me some rope.
I have some balls of wool. Could you make me some rope?
That's a little more than I want to pay.
I will go and get some wool.

cabe0f81-c517-4535-adb6-62fada5d11ea.title: <player>
cabe0f81-c517-4535-adb6-62fada5d11ea.text: I will go and get some wool.

7cc3c3c2-8a53-4290-b1d3-c975f050fe5f.title: Ned
7cc3c3c2-8a53-4290-b1d3-c975f050fe5f.text:
Aye, you do that. Remember, it takes 4 balls of wool to
make strong rope.

0b3f3498-27f5-4630-98bf-38d44bd0206d.title: <player>
0b3f3498-27f5-4630-98bf-38d44bd0206d.text: That's a little more than I want to pay.

8c95da60-7aab-415c-8ba2-1e121d6ec083.title: Ned
8c95da60-7aab-415c-8ba2-1e121d6ec083.text:
Well, if you ever need rope that's the price. Sorry.
An old sailor needs money for a little drop o' rum.

7a4ea4c0-6c4f-4d15-bda1-4cce1513bab5.title: <player>
7a4ea4c0-6c4f-4d15-bda1-4cce1513bab5.text: Okay, please sell me some rope.

9e109060-9acc-4e59-a470-641c9c89c861.title: Ned
9e109060-9acc-4e59-a470-641c9c89c861.text: There you go, finest rope in Gielinor.

589d89d4-e496-4b9f-b961-bf2613b4113d.title: <player>
589d89d4-e496-4b9f-b961-bf2613b4113d.text: I have some balls of wool. Could you make me some rope?

ca617a70-ebb6-40f1-bd80-e65dedcf0e7a.title: <player>
ca617a70-ebb6-40f1-bd80-e65dedcf0e7a.text: Ned, could you make other things from wool?

4ca64d8f-0b09-4c2d-bf98-058413e39721.title: Ned
4ca64d8f-0b09-4c2d-bf98-058413e39721.text: I am sure I can. What are you thinking of?

options.text: Could you knit me a sweater?
How about some sort of a wig?
Could you repair the arrow holes in the back of my shirt?

b509badf-8584-4eea-bca5-d3085f2ad339.title: <player>
b509badf-8584-4eea-bca5-d3085f2ad339.text:
Could you repair the arrow holes in the
back of my shirt?

3228b374-80ac-40f0-9b55-b96a96f565e6.title: Ned
3228b374-80ac-40f0-9b55-b96a96f565e6.text:
Ah yes, it's a tough world these days. There's a few
brave enough to attack from 10 metres away.

fac08b96-cc0b-48ae-a05f-78505b1a6fc7.title: Ned
fac08b96-cc0b-48ae-a05f-78505b1a6fc7.text: There you go, good as new.

fdbfb4a2-00fc-45bd-bc89-fcbbdac32587.title: <player>
fdbfb4a2-00fc-45bd-bc89-fcbbdac32587.text:
Thanks Ned. Maybe next time they will
attack me face to face.

c7ce5c23-64c4-4040-ad11-5431bc26a4f5.title: <player>
c7ce5c23-64c4-4040-ad11-5431bc26a4f5.text: Could you knit me a sweater?

5ab825aa-2900-49f7-8cb3-9307e6ede71a.title: Ned
5ab825aa-2900-49f7-8cb3-9307e6ede71a.text:
Do I look like a member of a sewing circle?
Be off wi' you. I have fought monsters
that would turn your hair blue.

f1bdc4e0-9bd9-4a8e-9d8d-5b03a0467f47.title: Ned
f1bdc4e0-9bd9-4a8e-9d8d-5b03a0467f47.text:
I don't need to be laughed at just 'cos I am getting
a bit old.

e8e3bea2-3971-49ec-b78e-7889d8a17a76.title: <player>
e8e3bea2-3971-49ec-b78e-7889d8a17a76.text: How about some sort of a wig?

8a9068d0-9f9f-45cf-8eeb-4174f33812f1.title: Ned
8a9068d0-9f9f-45cf-8eeb-4174f33812f1.text:
Well... That's an interesting thought. Yes, I think I
could do something. Give me 3 balls of wool and I
might be able to do it.

options.text: I have that now. Please, make me a wig.
I will come back when I need you to make me one.

6247aa55-484c-4fca-94c3-04c7de50f101.title: <player>
6247aa55-484c-4fca-94c3-04c7de50f101.text: I will come back when I need you to make me one.

59f5254b-b666-4085-9f7e-62f830c373d3.title: Ned
59f5254b-b666-4085-9f7e-62f830c373d3.text:
Well, it sounds like a challenge. Come to me if you
need one.

fc3e9a92-0942-4660-be08-4fcc5df56236.title: <player>
fc3e9a92-0942-4660-be08-4fcc5df56236.text: I have that now. Please, make me a wig.

b4af7120-fdb6-435a-88e9-45b97a788058.title: Ned
b4af7120-fdb6-435a-88e9-45b97a788058.text: Okay, I will have a go.

12396415-4bce-4251-9186-a471396d1045.title: Ned
12396415-4bce-4251-9186-a471396d1045.text:
Here you go, how's that for a quick effort?
Not bad I think!

a913efa3-cb3b-4587-b01a-5d08b62925b7.title: Ned
a913efa3-cb3b-4587-b01a-5d08b62925b7.text: You don't have enough coins to buy any rope!

4519ecdd-a626-4a91-95e1-8a7caf9683a9.title: Ned
4519ecdd-a626-4a91-95e1-8a7caf9683a9.text: You don't have enough wool to make any rope!
